"系统级缓存可安全重建，但位于系统目录需管理员权限，删除不经废纸篓——默认不勾选，确认后再清。" = "System-level caches rebuild safely, but they live in system directories: admin rights required and deletion bypasses the Trash — unselected by default, confirm before cleaning.";
"系统自管 purgeable" = "System-managed purgeable";
"缓存只为加速重复操作而存在，删除后应用会按需自动重建。已排除 Homebrew/包管理器与浏览器等由专项规则管理的目录。" = "Caches exist only to speed up repeat operations; apps rebuild them on demand. Homebrew/package-manager and browser directories governed by dedicated rules are excluded.";
"部分已释放空间可能被 APFS 本地快照暂存，系统通常会在 24 小时内自动归还；也可在「维护」页立即瘦身快照。" = "Some freed space may be held temporarily by APFS local snapshots; the system usually returns it within 24 hours. You can also thin snapshots now from the Maintenance page.";

